headline: Princess Cruises Toasts Top Wine Honors with 16 Wine Spectator Awards of Excellence for 2025
summary: Princess Cruises is once again raising a glass to excellence, as all 16 ships in its fleet have earned the prestigious Wine Spectator Award of Excellence in the publication's 2025 Restaurant Awards. Now a two-time winner, 15 Princess main dining rooms were recognized, alongside the Sanctuary Collection restaurant on Sun Princess, more than any other cruise line.
